unittitle_ssm: Jennifer (Sudie) Nostrand Papers
abstract_ssm: Jennifer (Sudie) Nostrand is a New York poet whose work has been published in literary magazines such as The California Quarterly, The Greensboro Review, and the Manhattan Poetry Review. Nostrand earned her Ph.D. in English Literature from New York University. The Jennifer (Sudie) Nostrand Papers largely consist of published copies of Nostrand's poetry from 1965 to 2013, with a selection of unpublished materials related to the editing, publication, or review of her work.
